# URL where the fh-portfolio-inner app is served.
# - Dev default (when unset): http://localhost:5174 — start the inner project with `npm run dev`.
# - Prod default (when unset): /inner/ — assumes you build fh-portfolio-inner into public/inner/.
# Override here if you host the inner app somewhere else.
# VITE_INNER_URL=http://localhost:5174
